propArrow: If `true`, adds an arrow to the tooltip.
propClasses: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
propDescribeChild:
Set to `true` if the `title` acts as an accessible description.
By default the `title` acts as an accessible label for the child.
propDisableFocusListener: Do not respond to focus events.
propDisableHoverListener: Do not respond to hover events.
propDisableInteractive:
Makes a tooltip not interactive, i.e. it will close when the user
hovers over the tooltip before the `leaveDelay` is expired.
propDisableTouchListener: Do not respond to long press touch events.
propEnterDelay:
The number of milliseconds to wait before showing the tooltip.
This prop won't impact the enter touch delay (`enterTouchDelay`).
propEnterNextDelay: The number of milliseconds to wait before showing the tooltip when one was already recently opened.
propEnterTouchDelay: The number of milliseconds a user must touch the element before showing the tooltip.
propFollowCursor: If `true`, the tooltip follow the cursor over the wrapped element.
propId:
This prop is used to help implement the accessibility logic.
If you don't provide this prop. It falls back to a randomly generated id.
propLeaveDelay:
The number of milliseconds to wait before hiding the tooltip.
This prop won't impact the leave touch delay (`leaveTouchDelay`).
propLeaveTouchDelay: The number of milliseconds after the user stops touching an element before hiding the tooltip.
propOnClose: Callback fired when the component requests to be closed.
propOnOpen: Callback fired when the component requests to be open.
propPopperComponent: The component used for the popper.
propTitle: Tooltip title. Zero-length titles string are never displayed.
propTransitionComponent:
The component used for the transition.
[Follow this guide](/components/transitions/#transitioncomponent-prop) to learn more about the requirements for this component.
propTransitionProps:
Props applied to the transition element.
By default, the element is based on this [`Transition`](http://reactcommunity.org/react-transition-group/transition) component.
stylesPopper: Styles applied to the Popper component.
stylesPopperInteractive: Styles applied to the Popper component unless `disableInteractive={true}`.
stylesPopperArrow: Styles applied to the Popper component if `arrow={true}`.
stylesTooltip: Styles applied to the tooltip (label wrapper) element.
stylesTooltipArrow: Styles applied to the tooltip (label wrapper) element if `arrow={true}`.
stylesArrow: Styles applied to the arrow element.
stylesTouch: Styles applied to the tooltip (label wrapper) element if the tooltip is opened by touch.
stylesTooltipPlacementLeft: Styles applied to the tooltip (label wrapper) element if `placement` contains "left".
stylesTooltipPlacementRight: Styles applied to the tooltip (label wrapper) element if `placement` contains "right".
stylesTooltipPlacementTop: Styles applied to the tooltip (label wrapper) element if `placement` contains "top".
stylesTooltipPlacementBottom: Styles applied to the tooltip (label wrapper) element if `placement` contains "bottom".
